# Omelette Project Overview

Omelette is a scientific literature lifecycle management system with 8 modules:
1. Keyword Management — three-level hierarchy + LLM expansion + search formula
2. Multi-Source Search — Semantic Scholar, OpenAlex, arXiv, Crossref
3. Deduplication — DOI + title similarity + LLM verification
4. Incremental Subscription — RSS/API updates
5. PDF Crawler — Unpaywall + multi-channel fallback
6. OCR Processing — pdfplumber (native) + PaddleOCR (scanned)
7. RAG Knowledge Base — ChromaDB + hybrid retrieval + LLM answers
8. Writing Assistant — summarize, cite, outline, gap analysis

## Stack
- Backend: FastAPI + SQLAlchemy async + SQLite + ChromaDB + Pydantic v2
- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + TailwindCSS v4
- Docs: VitePress (bilingual EN/ZH)
- CI: GitHub Actions, pre-commit hooks (ruff, conventional commits)

